name: The Inner Circle
Text: 'Deploy on Conference Room (only at start of game); deploy Sim Aloo here and (Virtual Block 4) There is No Try from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. Players may initiate battle here for free. Once per game may deploy Ord Mantell from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. May not be canceled (except by opponent) or placed in Used Pile. Immune to Ineffective Manuever.',
